						 <p>&#8230;Wait, that's a GoI? XD How specific!</p> <blockquote> <p>SCP-3254-1 has shown an extreme fondness for bear shaped plush toys, and uses them to create SCP-3254-1 instances.</p> </blockquote> <p>I think the first -1 isn't supposed to be there. Otherwise, might be a tad sappy, but I liked it. +1</p> 
				 	]]>
