					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5601261#post-3749829</guid>
				<title>Author Post</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5601261/scp-3254#post-3749829</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 26 Mar 2018 04:25:45 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>MayD</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1422059</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p><em>When was the last time you called your mother and said that you loved her?</em></p> </blockquote> <p>I wrote this SCP to explore the relationship between a mother who prioritizes work over family, and her grief in doing so. This is the second SCP from Grant's Zoo for Cybernetically Enhanced Bears, previously seen in <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-2579">SCP-2579</a>.</p> <p>Thank you to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/floppyphoenix" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1522038345" alt="FloppyPhoenix" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/floppyphoenix" >FloppyPhoenix</a></span> for crit.</p> <p>Image credit: <a href="https://pxhere.com/en/photo/738496">https://pxhere.com/en/photo/738496</a></p> 
				 	]]>
